{"tid":2009989,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【鐵證如山】林鄭政府派發「銅芯抗疫口罩」毒害市民  可致肺纖維化","createTime":"2020-05-10T06:49:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T06:49:17.000Z","uid":293677,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bce65cfd630038756a5b98bcc816293518978dd1","tid":2009989,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T06:49:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【鐵證如山  不容抵賴】</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新聞節錄：<br />\n<br />\n＂原則上銅金屬可用於殺菌，但其安全風險不容忽視。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">浸大化學系助理教授任康寧指，納米顆粒懸浮在空氣中將有機會被人體吸入，若數量較大外來物體已可破壞肺部組織，導致肺部纖維化</span></span>，「納米金屬吸入肺部對人體的健康風險，目前研究結果還不夠全面，存在爭論，但一般認為對心血管系統有威脅，毫克級別吸入量已算數量較大了。」惟他亦強調，毫克級別的吸入量通常長期積累，而非短時間就能聚集。＂<br />\n<br />\n＂<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港大化學博士鄺士山（K Kwong）直指，納米銅比起使用在劣質口罩的玻璃纖維更大傷害，肺部吸入微粒子有機會致死，「顧及自己的身體健康，我一定不會用含銅的口罩。」</span></span>以銅殺菌的效能已獲公認，惟多名學者均就其對抗冠狀病毒的成效抱存疑慮。＂<br />\n<br />\n原文刊於《星島日報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1764967/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%81%90%E6%B0%A7%E5%8C%96%E9%8A%85%E5%90%B8%E5%85%A5%E8%82%BA%E9%83%A8-%E9%8A%85%E8%8A%AF%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E6%8E%80%E7%86%B1%E8%AD%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1764967%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%25B0%25A7%25E5%258C%2596%25E9%258A%2585%25E5%2590%25B8%25E5%2585%25A5%25E8%2582%25BA%25E9%2583%25A8-%25E9%258A%2585%25E8%258A%25AF%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E6%258E%2580%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25AD%25B0&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpUV6NNh9RYlaag4wFuTDRgw%3D&h=f437f0eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1764967%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%25B0%25A7%25E5%258C%2596%25E9%258A%2585%25E5%2590%25B8%25E5%2585%25A5%25E8%2582%25BA%25E9%2583%25A8-%25E9%258A%2585%25E8%258A%25AF%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E6%258E%2580%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25AD%25B0&h=a29f9ab5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1764967/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%81%90%E6%B0%A7%E5%8C%96%E9%8A%85%E5%90%B8%E5%85%A5%E8%82%BA%E9%83%A8-%E9%8A%85%E8%8A%AF%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E6%8E%80%E7%86%B1%E8%AD%B0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭政府邊可能咁好心<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「<del>銅</del><span style=\"color: red;\">黑</span>芯抗疫口罩」</span>毒害市民<br />\n港共政府亡我之心不死"}]}